Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Carolina Premier Properties
Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Treasure II

data.description: Great investor opportunity to get into this beautiful home and neighborhood of Chadwick Shores. One way in and out with security gate (11pm-5am). Community river access with picnic area and dock. Kayaks and Canoes welcome! 10 minutes to Beach, Stone Bay and Back Gate. Also at the end of Bayshore Drive is a neighborhood park with swings, play-set and covered pic-nic area with grill.  Tons of natural light throughout this home. Living room features a gas logged fireplace and built in TV niche above fireplace. Kitchen is complete with stainless steel appliance package, pantry and pass thru to the living room. Sliding door to rear deck overlooking the tree lined fenced in yard. Separate dining area. 2 car side entry garage with floored attic access. Master bedroom features a trey ceiling with a private on-suite that includes his/her sinks, deep soaking tub, private shower w/ door and walk in closet. Huge 4th bedroom with an additional 5x9 jet out.  Upstairs laundry. New Roof 2019 and New HVAC systems 2022. Tenant Occupied until 2.25.24.
